<h2>Navigation</h2>
<p>Accessible navigation menus implementing the <a href="https://www.w3.org/WAI/ARIA/apg/patterns/disclosure/examples/disclosure-navigation/">W3C APG Disclosure Navigation</a> pattern. Provides keyboard navigation via roving tabindex, collapsible sections with <code>aria-expanded</code>, and router integration with <code>aria-current="page"</code> tracking.</p>

<p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-text-muted);">
  <strong>Terminology:</strong> See <a href="/semantics/">Semantics & Glossary</a> for terms like <a href="/semantics/#term-disclosure">disclosure</a>, <a href="/semantics/#term-navigation-landmark">navigation landmark</a>, and <a href="/semantics/#term-aria-current">aria-current</a>.
</p>

